        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10"><p class="text-amber-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">👁️ VISIBLE</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">12 pts · 7 letters · V=4+I+S+IBLE · Bingo</p></div>
