        <p class="text-base text-gray-200">There are fewer -IBLE words than -ABLE words, but <span class="text-white font-medium">the average score per -IBLE word is higher</span>. FLEXIBLE alone (20pts + 50 bingo = 70) is worth memorizing the entire -IBLE list for.</p>
      </div>

